to rejoice despite any mental or emotional distress

00:43:32.900 --> 00:43:36.900
that you may be experiencing even now?

00:43:36.900 --> 00:43:39.900
Is it your relationship with Jehovah?

00:43:39.900 --> 00:43:40.900
The Brotherhood?

00:43:40.900 --> 00:43:42.900
Our hope?

00:43:42.900 --> 00:43:45.900
Or is it something else?

00:43:45.900 --> 00:43:53.210
In addition to the provisions from Jehovah, consider these practical suggestions.

00:43:54.210 --> 00:43:58.210
Maintain a healthy diet.

00:43:58.210 --> 00:44:02.210
Couple with that, get sufficient rest

00:44:02.210 --> 00:44:06.210
and get a measure of exercise.

00:44:06.210 --> 00:44:09.210
Now, you can make two lists.

00:44:09.210 --> 00:44:12.210
One of the problems that you can solve

00:44:12.210 --> 00:44:18.210
and the other problems you cannot solve at present.

00:44:18.210 --> 00:44:23.210
Act on the first list and leave the rest in Jehovah's hands.

00:44:23.210 --> 00:44:28.969
Talk things out with an elder,

00:44:28.969 --> 00:44:32.969
or perhaps a mature friend, someone you're close to,

00:44:32.969 --> 00:44:35.969
and a parent.

00:44:35.969 --> 00:44:41.969
These are there to help us, and they're ready and willing

00:44:41.969 --> 00:44:45.969
to share the knowledge and understanding that they have

00:44:45.969 --> 00:44:49.969
and they'll do it generously with you.

00:44:49.969 --> 00:44:52.969
Realize that some forms of mental distress

00:44:52.969 --> 00:44:55.969
